OL,3,CCommonwealth can remain 'force for
OL,4,Cgood' if nations work together, King
OL,5,Cto say
OL,7,FThe King will tell the Commonwealth
OL,8,Fthat by "working together" member
OL,9,Fnations can ensure the institution
OL,10,Fremains a "force for good".
OL,12,FIn his message marking Commonwealth
OL,13,FDay, Charles will say it is when
OL,14,Fcountry's face testing moments, like
OL,15,F"conflict, climate change and rapid
OL,16,Ftransformation", that the family of
OL,17,Fnations' "enduring spirit" comes to
OL,18,Fthe fore.
