OL,3,CCommonwealth can remain 'force for
OL,4,Cgood' if nations work together, King
OL,5,Cto say
OL,7,FCommonwealth Day will be celebrated on
OL,8,FMonday and marked by an annual service
OL,9,Fat Westminster Abbey attended by
OL,10,Fsenior members of the royal family,
OL,11,Fleading politicians and diplomats
OL,12,Famong a congregation of 1,800.
OL,14,FSpice Girl Geri Halliwell-Horner, an
OL,15,Fambassador for the Royal Commonwealth
OL,16,FSociety which stages the event, will
OL,17,Fgive an address and there will be a
OL,18,Freflection from former Strictly Come
OL,19,FDancing judge Oti Mabuse and a poem
OL,20,Ffrom Selina Tusitala Marsh, the
OL,21,Finaugural Commonwealth poet laureate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773052871
OL,3,CCommonwealth can remain 'force for
OL,4,Cgood' if nations work together, King
OL,5,Cto say
OL,7,FThe King says in an extract from his
OL,8,Fwritten message, released in full on
OL,9,FSunday: "We join together on this
OL,10,FCommonwealth Day at a time of great
OL,11,Fchallenge and great possibility.
OL,13,F"Across our world, communities and
OL,14,Fnations face the increasing pressures
OL,15,Fof conflict, climate change and rapid
OL,16,Ftransformation.
OL,18,F"Yet it is often in such testing
OL,19,Fmoments that the enduring spirit of
OL,20,Fthe Commonwealth is most clearly
OL,21,Frevealed."
OL,26,@qD@IOUuD@AOUzD@AOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
