OL,3,CCommonwealth can remain 'force for
OL,4,Cgood' if nations work together, King
OL,5,Cto say
OL,7,FConflicts continue to rage across the
OL,8,Fworld from Ukraine to Sudan and more
OL,9,Frecently the war waged by American and
OL,10,FIsraeli forces in Iran, while
OL,11,Fscientists designated 2025 the third
OL,12,Fwarmest year on record and concerns
OL,13,Fmount about the prospect of AI.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
