OL,3,CCommonwealth can remain 'force for
OL,4,Cgood' if nations work together, King
OL,5,Cto say
OL,7,FThe King also says in his message:
OL,8,F"Working together, we can ensure that
OL,9,Fthe Commonwealth continues to stand as
OL,10,Fa force for good ` grounded in
OL,11,Fcommunity, committed to the kind of
OL,12,Frestorative sustainability that has a
OL,13,Freturn on investment, enriched by
OL,14,Fculture, steadfast in its care for our
OL,15,Fplanet, and united in friendship and
OL,16,Fin the service of its people."
OL,26,@pD@AOUxD@^O]
