OL,3,CCommonwealth can remain 'force for
OL,4,Cgood' if nations work together, King
OL,5,Cto say
OL,7,FAs head of the Commonwealth, Charles
OL,8,Fissues an annual message to the 56
OL,9,Fmember nations which will hold their
OL,10,Fbiennial meeting this year during the
OL,11,Ffirst week of November in the capital
OL,12,Fof Antigua and Barbuda.
OL,14,FInspired by the meeting's theme `
OL,15,Faccelerating partnerships and
OL,16,Finvestment for a prosperous
OL,17,FCommonwealth ` the service will
OL,18,Fcelebrate collaboration as the
OL,19,Fdefining strength of the modern family
OL,20,Fof nations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
