OL,3,CCommonwealth can remain 'force for
OL,4,Cgood' if nations work together, King
OL,5,Cto say
OL,7,FThe service will feature landmark
OL,8,Fartistic moments, including the world
OL,9,Fpremiere of the Commonwealth Symphony,
OL,10,Fcomposed by Rekesh Chauhan, and a
OL,11,Fbespoke dance collaboration between
OL,12,Fthe Royal Ballet School and Sapnay
OL,13,FEntertainments, uniting classical
OL,14,Fballet and Bollywood in a powerful
OL,15,Fexpression of cross-cultural
OL,16,Fpartnership.
OL,18,FOther performers include a Scottish
OL,19,Fceilidh band, the Melodians Steel
OL,20,FOrchestra and special reflections and
OL,21,Freadings from guests.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
